prompts.frontCover: Humorous birthday card front cover, flat 2D illustration in a flowing watercolor style with soft edges. An energetic and chaotic scene set against a snowy mountain backdrop, stylized with soft washes of blue and white. In the center, cartoon illustrated versions of Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo [fad5d29c-9bdf-49a0-8663-fb0907eb6d99] are comically attempting to snowboard together on a single, oversized snowboard. Jordan, wearing his dark t-shirt, is trying to balance while typing on a floating, semi-transparent laptop that has binary code (0s and 1s) trailing behind it like a ribbon. Lao Lao, in her white zip-up jacket, is laughing and holding onto his arm, trying to steer with a giant pair of chopsticks. Instead of snow, they are gliding down a river of food: beautifully painted watercolor illustrations of sushi rolls, perfectly seared wagyu steak slices, and Chinese dumplings are scattered all around them, creating a playful, delicious avalanche. The entire scene is dynamic, with lighthearted color splatters adding to the sense of fun and movement. Centered on the card, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Jordan!". Clean white background framing the watercolor illustration.
